When A critical security data pipeline disconnects or breaks, blinding the SOC to incoming attacks. Big tech hiring managers love to see cost/health operational queries.

// Track data ingestion volume anomalies across different log types over the past week
_SentinelHealth
| where TimeGenerated > ago(7d)
| where SentinelResourceType == "Analytics Rule"
| extend ExtendedProps = todynamic(ExtendedProperties)
| extend EventCount = toint(ExtendedProps.QueryResultAmount)
| summarize TotalRuns = count(), ZeroResultRuns = countif(EventCount == 0) by SentinelResourceName
| extend FailureRatePercentage = (todouble(ZeroResultRuns) / todouble(TotalRuns)) * 100
| order by FailureRatePercentage desc